===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm}} < {{etyl|ML.}} ''[[instrumentalis]]'' < ''[[instruere]]'' ("to build into, set up, construct, furnish," hence "to train") < ''[[in-]]'' ("on") + ''[[struere]]'' ("to put together, arrange, pile up, build, construct") < {{proto|Indo-European|streu-|to spread, extend, stretch out}}.

